org.rdkit.knime.nodes.open3dalignment

Class RDKitOpen3DAlignmentNodeDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • DefaultNodeSettingsPane
      • org.rdkit.knime.nodes.open3dalignment.RDKitOpen3DAlignmentNodeDialog

  • public class RDKitOpen3DAlignmentNodeDialog
extends DefaultNodeSettingsPane
    NodeDialog for the "RDKitOpen3DAlignment" Node. This node dialog derives from DefaultNodeSettingsPane which allows creation of a simple dialog with standard components. If you need a more complex dialog please derive directly from org.knime.core.node.NodeDialogPane.
    Author:
    Manuel Schwarze
